Hello mes amies, I hope everyone is enjoying their Sunday🐾🐺🐾. Sooo, mid April I bought two things.
*avoids eye contact and shoves snout between paws to hide eyes*
I purchased an absolutely exquisite charm from @delilasophia (to boot, it is a shop from just outside of where I was basically born and raised (stateside anyway)).
*flicks tail in excitement*
AAAND I purchased a CUSTOM collar from AlyKittenKreations (@shop__akk). It is so beautiful🤗.
*
I bought the charm first and the thing was, I only owned all dark/gothic collars. The collars either didn't have a spot to add a charm or if I added this charm it would definitely clash. So... oops. Ooor, opportunity?  Yeah, opportunity, you're right, that's exactly what I thought too. Besides, I was looking for a light collar for a long time anyway and this just gave me a bit of a shove😎.
*
I stumbled across one that was posted by Aly and I asked if she could customize it and she said yes. EEEE, giddiness set in. Her and I began talking about what would work, sizing and vwuaalaa! GORGEOUS! I 💝 it. It has a subtle beauty and elegance to it. I just adore the peek-a-boo of lavender. It came with an adorable little bell and cute crown charm as well. It fits just PERFECTLY! The stitching is durable too.
*
The charm I ordered from @delilasophia is so pretty and I think it goes perfect with my AlyKittenKreations collar. I feel as though they play wonderfully off each other🤗. This charm is a Dragon Scale charm. I of course got it in purple, but now I want it in every colour that I can get my paws on. I love that it feels like scales🙄. It adds an AWESOME element to it. I wasn't expecting the clasp to be so large and at first I thought it would bother me, but it really doesn't. I dont even notice it anymore, it's just apart of it now, ya know. Plus, it is easier to use than tiny clasps so it actually works out better that it is bigger. I also really LOVE how on top of the scales there is an iridescent aspect to them💞. The cute colored pearl bead is a sweet accent. This charm is VERY well made and sturdy.
*
